\f1\b\fs125\fsmilli62568 \cf0 IX. The Kingdom\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa351\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0\fs42\fsmilli21120 \cf0 The Kingdom of God includes both His general sovereignty over the universe and His particular kingship over men who willfully acknowledge Him as King. Particularly the Kingdom is the realm of salvation into which men enter by trustful, childlike commitment to Jesus Christ. Christians ought to pray and to labor that the Kingdom may come and God\'92s will be done on earth. The full consummation of the Kingdom awaits the return of Jesus Christ and the end of this age.\
